OL,3,C'It's no life': Pensioner spending
OL,4,C#150 a week to heat flat
OL,6,FA pensioner says she is spending #150
OL,7,Fa week on energy bills for her poorly
OL,8,Finsulated flat.
OL,10,FDiane Ashmore said she was paying out
OL,11,Fmore than half her pension just to
OL,12,Fstay warm at the property at Chevet
OL,13,FHouse, Doncaster.
OL,15,FThe 70-year-old said she often sees
OL,16,Fthe condensation from her breath as
OL,17,Fher flat, which has single brick
OL,18,Fwalls, is so cold and her clothes are
OL,19,Faffected by damp.
