OL,3,C'It's no life': Pensioner spending
OL,4,C#150 a week to heat flat
OL,6,FShe told ITV Calendar that she spends
OL,7,Fher evenings going to bed at 6pm and
OL,8,Fwatching TV under a quilt instead of
OL,9,Frelaxing in her living room.
OL,11,FMs Ashmore pays for her heating
OL,12,Fthrough a meter but is constantly
OL,13,Fhaving to top it up. Between 1
OL,14,FDecember and 1 March last year, she
OL,15,Fspent #3,500 on heating. In one two-
OL,16,Fday period, she spent #140.
OL,18,FNow the pensioner says she is
OL,19,Fterrified about her bills for the
OL,20,Fwinter ahead.
