OL,3,C'It's no life': Pensioner spending
OL,4,C#150 a week to heat flat
OL,6,F"I get #460 a fortnight, and it's
OL,7,Fcosting me #300 at least to heat this
OL,8,Fproperty," she said.
OL,10,F"I might as well open my window and
OL,11,Fthrow all my money out because that's
OL,12,Fwhere it's going."
OL,14,FMany of the neighbours living in the
OL,15,Fbuilding run by St Leger Homes
OL,16,FDoncaster say they are also paying
OL,17,Fextortionate amounts just to stay warm.
OL,19,FOne woman said she had resorted to
OL,20,Fheating and staying in a single room
OL,21,Fto keep costs down.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/7
