OL,3,C'It's no life': Pensioner spending
OL,4,C#150 a week to heat flat
OL,6,F"In this day and age you should be
OL,7,Fable to live in a comfortable, warm
OL,8,Fenvironment," Ms Ashmore added.
OL,10,F"I have to go to bed at six o'clock
OL,11,Fevery night to get under the duvet and
OL,12,Fget warm. I'm only 70, that's no life.
OL,13,FIt's no life living like this... I
OL,14,Ffeel like I'm knocking my head against
OL,15,Fa brick wall," she added.
OL,17,FMatt Copeland, from National Energy
OL,18,FAction, said new standards needed to
OL,19,Fbe set to improve the quality of
OL,20,Fhousing in the UK, particularly for
OL,21,Fpensioners.
