OL,3,C'It's no life': Pensioner spending
OL,4,C#150 a week to heat flat
OL,6,FHe said: "We have a very, very poor
OL,7,Fhousing stock in the UK and
OL,8,Funfortunately there are still homes
OL,9,Fthat are very inefficient.
OL,11,F"For those homes that are the leakiest
OL,12,Fthat require the most energy to keep
OL,13,Fwarm over the winter you can see these
OL,14,Fastronomical costs especially in
OL,15,Fhouseholds where the person needs to
OL,16,Fbe warmer than the typical household
OL,17,Fbecause of age-related issues or
OL,18,Fhealth-related issues."
