OL,3,C'It's no life': Pensioner spending
OL,4,C#150 a week to heat flat
OL,6,FHe added: "We need housing to be
OL,7,Fappropriate so that energy costs can
OL,8,Fremain affordable for people."
OL,10,FSt Leger Homes Doncaster, which runs
OL,11,FChevet House, said it was reviewing
OL,12,Fthe situation.
OL,14,FA spokesperson said: "We have recently
OL,15,Fcarried out surveys at Chevet House
OL,16,Fand we are reviewing the findings to
OL,17,Fdetermine what work may be recommended.
